Including working together now
--------------------------------
- Configuration server
- Eureka Naming Server
- Zuul Server
- Setting Service (representing lookups required by other business services). It include Caching for unchangeable lookups using Ehcache


Supported Features
--------------------------------
Servives Bus (Through RabbitMQ)
Sleuth & Zipkin Client Logging (Through RabbitMQ)


Next step
--------------------------------
- News services will work and call endpoints in setting server through Zuul using Feign Clients
- Authentication Server (UAA)  with not allow unauthenticated requests

Required to run the solution
--------------------------------
1- Install zipkin server : https://zipkin.io/
2- Install  RabbitMQ : https://www.rabbitmq.com/download.html
